			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2277213">
									

<p>I actually have a list of notes about how she works on my <a href="http://sandbox.scp-wiki.net/y">sandbox</a> that is longer than the actual story.</p>
<p>It's not an ability at all; she's just clones.</p>
<p>Officially, she's an actual research assistant who volunteered for an experimental cloning program for the ethics committee, as a way of investigating options more morally acceptable than D-class usage. Rumors in the Foundation say she's either an entirely artificial person or a fem-clone of O5-8.</p>

